==============================================================================
c2.patch.jasplitter
==============================================================================



Installation
------------

Install c2.patch.jasplitter by adding it to your buildout::

    [buildout]

    ...

    eggs =
        c2.patch.jasplitter


and then running ``bin/buildout``

----------

- Issue Tracker: https://bitbucket.org/cmscom/c2.patch.jasplitter/admin/issues
